# An [[administrative]] [[subdivision]] of [[imperial]], [[republican]], and [[communist]] [[China]], [[typically]] [[translated]] as "[[county]]" but [[now]] [[generally]] [[restrict]]ed to [[rural]] [[area]]s, [[contrast]]ed with the [[urban]] "[[district]]s" ({{zh-l|*區}})
